{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigrationGuides"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"role":"article","roleHeading":"Article","modules":[{"name":"ComposableArchitecture"}],"title":"Migrating to 1.16"},"kind":"article","primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"There are no steps needed to migrate to 1.16 of the Composable Architecture, but there has been"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a change to the underlying behavior of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".appStorage"},{"type":"text","text":" that one should be aware of. When using"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".appStorage"},{"type":"text","text":" with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@Shared"},{"type":"text","text":", if your key does not contain the characters “.” or “@”, then changes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to that key in "},{"code":"UserDefaults","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be observed using key-value observing (KVO)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Otherwise, "},{"code":"NotificationCenter","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be used to observe changes."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"KVO is a far more efficient way of observing changes to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UserDefaults"},{"type":"text","text":" and it works cross-process,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as from widgets and app extensions. However, KVO does not work when the keys contain “.”"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or “@”, and so in those cases we must use the cruder tool of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NotificationCenter"},{"type":"text","text":". That is not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as efficient, and it forces us to perform a thread-hop when the notification is posted before"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"we can update the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@Shared"},{"type":"text","text":" value. For this reason it is not possible to animate changes that are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"made directly to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UserDefaults"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"code":["withAnimation {","  \/\/ ⚠️ This will not animate any SwiftUI views using '@Shared(.appStorage(\"co.pointfree.count\"))'","  UserDefaults.standard.set(0, forKey: \"co.pointfree.count\")","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In general, we recommend using other delimeters for your keys, such as “\/”, “:”, “-”, etc.:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["@Shared(.appStorage(\"co:pointfree:count\")) var count = 0"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/composablearchitecture\/migratingto1.16"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.19","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.18","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17.1","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.15","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.14","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.13","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.12","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.11